Pamela Bellwood https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pamela_Bellwood 0 Pamela Bellwood (born Pamela Anne King on June 26, 1951) is an American actress best known for her role as Claudia Blaisdel Carrington on the 1980s prime time soap opera, Dynasty.
